<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Artists_using_virtual_reality_technology">Artists using virtual reality technology</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Virtual_reality&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Artists using virtual reality technology">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="div-col columns column-width" style="-moz-column-width: 30em; -webkit-column-width: 30em; column-width: 30em;">
<ul>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rebecca_Allen" title="Rebecca Allen">Rebecca Allen</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maurice_Benayoun" title="Maurice Benayoun">Maurice Benayoun</a></li>
